summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Parks and Recreation, accepting a deed to certain property within the Plat of Lakewood, a replat of Maynard's Lake Washington Addition as per plat recorded in Volume 10 of Plats, page 46, Records of King County, Washington; AND Maynard's Lake Washington Addition as per plat recorded in Volume 2, page 33, Records of King County, Washington; TOGETHER WITH portions of vacated streets adjoining, and placing said property under the jurisdiction of the Department of Parks and Recreation.
